{"tid":1124237,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"想比較下Avengers 3同 Avengers 4","createTime":"2019-04-25T02:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T00:30:31.000Z","uid":212942,"like":18,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ee658a654b890ad32807a2dc80a81e6d26958bee","tid":1124237,"uid":212942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T02:14:19.000Z","msg":"主要想講下我對第3集同第4集比較嘅睇法<br />\n有錯誤邏輯同觀念 麻煩你地指教一下小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望可以屌我屌得細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">以下內容涉及劇透情節</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nInfinity War逐粒石都交代點拎(除咗power stone)<br />\n每拎一粒都會有啲場面可以睇到<br />\n掟gamora 殺loki 殺vision <br />\n喺knowhere又睇到thanos同個女嘅關係<br />\n喺titan 打交有反高潮 比觀眾假希望<br />\n又有講無限手套點樣整出嚟<br />\n笑點都多少少(個人特別鍾意drax嘅笑位)<br />\n<br />\n但係endgame每粒石都拎得好快手咁...<br />\n現實寶石直頭講都無講就搞掂...<br />\n比較好啲嘅都係拎mind stone同space stone..<br />\n多返啲情節同埋多少少梗玩下<br />\n然後唔知點樣就整到隻無限手套出嚟<br />\n<br />\n我覺得如果由劇情去睇<br />\n因為Infinity War主角係Thanos一個咁滯<br />\n易啲將所有嘢講細啲 所以會好睇啲<br />\n<br />\n但係如果由一個Marvel忠實fans睇<br />\nEndgame包含晒咁多條線嘅感情同性格發展<br />\ne.g Captain America 同 Iron Man和好<br />\nBlack Widow犧牲小我 成就大我<br />\nIron man同 Spiderman之間嘅關係<br />\n仲有一大堆串聯以前嘅嘢<br />\nI am Iron man<br />\nI can do this all day<br />\nHail Hydra 等等<br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得endgame勝在<br />\n引起到大家嘅共鳴感而出色<br />\n同埋都有唔少驚喜元素<br />\ne.g captain america 拎起thor 個錘<br />\nCaptain America再嗌一次 Avengers Assemble <br />\n真係瀨晒精出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nIron Man 犧牲自己嘅覺悟<br />\ncaptain america同到條女一齊 等等<br />\n<br />\n不過我覺得endgame都有少少失色嘅係<br />\n1.時間限制 交代唔到太多<br />\n<br />\n2.black widow同hulk嘅感情線個尾埋得唔好<br />\n如果拎soul stone嗰part係hulk 掟black widow落去<br />\n會震撼過hawkeye 掟會落去<br />\n<br />\n3.Captain Marvel完全同Avengers班人零抵觸咁<br />\n仲要比人當咗做打手 有事鍾無豔 無事夏迎春嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n4.Captain Marvel套戲營造到佢同Nick Fury好friend<br />\n但居然喺呢套嘢臨尾企埋一齊 都無俾到個shot佢地吹下水<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">完全個人意見部分</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n5.屌你老母Russell Brothers因為自己鍾意Falcom<br />\n將Captain America傳比佢 而唔係做咗3集Captain America重要人物嘅Winter Soldier<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">嗰陣係咁期待falcom話自己受唔起 比bucky<br />\n點知個仆街闔家翁真係拎咗 即刻燥咗少少</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟不才 並唔係由一開波Iron Man 1已經開始追Marvel睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但翻煲晒所有miss咗嘅戲 學多啲梗同埋角色嘅發展<br />\n好想了解多啲MCU文化同背景 <br />\n覺得好得意同埋希好多嘢值得去期待<br />\ne.g dormammu 背景 <br />\n同埋 Quill 老豆嗰個天神族嘅人 到底可以有幾勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再次希望咁多位資深Marvel迷可以指正我了解不足嘅地方<br />\n屌細力啲 <br />\n同埋想一齊討論下嚟緊MCU嘅發展電影<br />\netc 永恒族, 新星Nova, 同埋嚟緊Spiderman等等嘅戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c431ee6860954cf3bccbfc540cbe15e97facd65e","tid":1124237,"uid":212942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T02:44:33.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b09dbd2e90a8b0a0a2b17f53da7d3977b6d2b30f","tid":1124237,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T03:38:29.000Z","msg":"見你咁真心幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過啲fans應該係晒劇透post到"},{"pid":"37d8ff3e9a6db0ba851bfe73cc189259d4938068","tid":1124237,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"ee658a654b890ad32807a2dc80a81e6d26958bee","tid":1124237,"uid":212942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T02:14:19.000Z","msg":"主要想講下我對第3集同第4集比較嘅睇法<br />\n有錯誤邏輯同觀念 麻煩你地指教一下小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f